WEBVTT

00:00.259 --> 00:02.711
Honestly, my kids were always on my laptop.

00:03.157 --> 00:06.187
I didn't think I could buy them their own, let alone for under 300 dollars,...

00:06.485 --> 00:09.535
...but this ASUS with Windows is lightweight and has everything they need,...

00:09.999 --> 00:12.053
...not like Chromebooks that can't install Office...

00:12.137 --> 00:14.533
...or have to be connected to the Internet to get much done.

00:15.045 --> 00:17.953
With this, they can do homework, chat, play games,...

00:18.216 --> 00:19.987
...on their own laptop on their own time.

00:20.584 --> 00:21.471
So no more fighting,...

00:22.438 --> 00:24.095
...at least not over my laptop.

